Revision history for Perl extension Math::Fractal::DLA.

0.21  Sun Jan  9 18:00:00 2005
        - Removed a bug in setBaseColor that prevented the module to set the colors correctly
        - Added an inherit flag in the Mason example files
        - Included the Log::SimpleLog module
        - Renamed ErrorExit to exitOnError
        - Added support for Module::Build
        - Added a basic test file
        - Added an example script that can be configured with a XML file

0.20  Fri Oct 11 00:01:00 2002
	- moved the different types in own modules (eg sub explode => Explode.pm)
	- better log handling
	- using croak instead of die
	- added hash parameters to the methods with multiple parameters
	- performance improvement in Explode-mode

0.10  Sun Jun  9 20:00:00 2002
	- original version


